    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and I want to give any potential buyer a completely honest picture of what they're getting. This car has significant issues that need to be clearly understood before purchase. It does start and run, but it requires substantial mechanical attention \u2014 expect worn components, possible engine or transmission concerns, and cosmetic damage throughout. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery, cracked trim, and non-functional features. The exterior has visible rust, dents, and fading paint. This is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. There are no warranties implied or offered. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing \u2014 what you see is what you get, and I want you to go in with clear expectations.",
