    },
    {
      "id": "standard_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_2",
      "description": "2019 Honda Accord EX-L in good condition. The engine and mechanical systems are functioning well with no major issues, though the car has normal wear consistent with its age. The interior shows some light wear but no significant damage or staining. Overall a solid, reliable vehicle.",
      "price": 34000.0,
